Here, we are adding NDVI temporal trends and CSV export functionality to the WebGIS.

You will learn how to:

✔ Build a 5-year NDVI time series using Earth Engine
✔ Calculate monthly mean NDVI values
✔ Display NDVI trends in a Chart.js line chart
✔ Connect Flask backend with frontend chart visualization
✔ Export NDVI values as a CSV file
✔ Analyze vegetation changes over time for any uploaded ROI
